</activity>

<activity><title>Compound Interest</title>
<introduction><p>Cyril would like to invest $5000 for two years in a money market account that pays interest compounded annually.</p>
</introduction>

<task><p>Write a formula for the balance, <m>B</m>, of Cyril's account after two years in terms of the interest rate, <m>r</m>.</p></task>

